cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.FL, cs.SC 

The paper deals with techniques to prove termination of string rewriting on cycles, which involves formal language theory and logic. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also involves techniques related to programming languages (cs.PL), data structures (cs.DS), formal languages (cs.FL), and computational complexity (cs.SC).
